{
  "name": "Rhythmboat Cruises",
  "formatted_address": "King Street Wharf, King St, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia",
  "location": {
    "lat": -33.8686058,
    "lng": 151.2018206
  },
  "formatted_phone_number": "1300 551 804",
  "website": "http://www.rhythmboat.com.au/",
  "rating": 3.9,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Antoinette Farmer",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101452787798154091484/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFS8yJBq8FQv4hnEdV9jCCKmd-IJFwY-Kfhiy41TjvrQoih-jN=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "9 months ago",
      "text": "Well I was not expecting much when I booked the Christmas cruise, being only $65 ahead, But I was very impressed , the tables were nicely set up with white table cloths, and some simple but nice Christmas decorations, First was coffee or tea with tasty treats, then the main meal , nicely cooked chicken and gravy, some prawns, ham off the bone,  baked veges, and salad, fallowed by plum pudding with custard and ice cream, we saw about 6 dolphins! Christmas music, not too loud, 3 hours among the canals and river, compÃ¨re was great very witty, thanks for a great day! Weâ€™ll be back ! Happy Christmas!",
      "time": 1733914042,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "lynette loydall",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111833575986578243875/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUc5cbJdPYDUrY9H0wCYirLHk05zqbzzgfdeXub8ib6gqMPjEI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "8 years ago",
      "text": "What a FANTASTIC Night,  we booked the Rhythmboat for our Vivid cruise what a night we had. From the time we boarded the boat to the time we left. Staff were great, everybody raved about the food, Elvis was great. We danced, laughed and sang through the night, all our need were catered for.  We will definitely be booking the Rhythmboat again.  Our booking was for 114 people, I can't speak highly enough about the staff, from my first phone call, I felt welcome from the start.",
      "time": 1498533190,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Luke Feledy",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104931044357512972928/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxWkLeBzZXPHEqybkIV88cq7oOIvBNE3hz5hBYeqICO1_tfkw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "6 years ago",
      "text": "I have been on the Rythmboat for a few cruises, they never disappoint! The food is amazing, the staff are always friendly and go out of their way to help everyone, and the entertainment is great!\n\nThe ABBA tribute show is a must! Having been on a few of them, we decided to book the whole boat and show out for our mums 50th. Everyone dressed up 70s style and it was a hilarious night. She had the most amazing time, the crew let us jump onboard early to set up some decorations and the band had everyone dancing late into the night.\n\nI highly recommend going to one of these cruises, or booking the boat out privately. Nothing is better than an evening cruising around Sydney Harbour in great company and a drink in hand. Always a good time!",
      "time": 1557820234,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Litessa L",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107846767826057612861/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxS2ONdREWbx8WSIWeHCEXTjvzUdiJrCDzE56CgjqgWZXXRsg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 1,
      "relative_time_description": "7 years ago",
      "text": "I've been on many show cruises on the harbour...As soon as the boat arrived I could immediately tell I would be in for a very disappointing night,  unfortunately I did not have a choice on what boat cruise to pick due to this being a group event, though if I did,  I definitely would not pick this boat.  This cruise was the worst I've ever been on. The food was terrible,  Entertainment was boring,  very dissapointed about how the staff handle crowd interaction segments of their show.  This killed the entire Vivid experience for my family and I.",
      "time": 1528766340,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "marienne shepherd",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101974769043781856701/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH3V_oV_aJ5_sVl2YvJOdHTQ1P5waAuQzxYJ4qzL64xqU43Cc-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "8 years ago",
      "text": "This is an email I received for our show \"A Touch of opera\": Hi Marienne .... just wanted to forward my/our appreciation and congratulations for a wonderful evening last night ...we thoroughly enjoyed ourselves.\n\nPlease pass on my appreciation and congratulations to Susie, Robert, Christian, the pianist, as well as John and the crew (and of course yourself).\n\nThe last couple of years has taken me to some emotionally dark places and so for me, the pleasure of some of your operatic pieces caused me some emotionally tear provoking moments, but also some great laughs.\n\nI hope you run these sort of events again, as I am sure I will be able to gain more interest from our wine club next time.\n\nKind regards ... Billy x",
      "time": 1490578071,
      "translated": false
    }
  ],
