  },
  "formatted_phone_number": "(02) 9374 4000",
  "website": "http://google.com/",
  "rating": 4.1,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Kimberly",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111489942672080667408/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8OoDX9NJrD8z8m9sLoCpbMaLr1QAp-sslCBUL2kf1A0uSlyUOyw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "Best service I've ever received my son absolutely loves his therapist  you could not go wrong choosing open play therapy. They have well trained therapist that are highly educated that bond and work to suit your Childs needs.",
      "time": 1756788437,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "8",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118208933162619130533/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAztO-LgetXYkSRoKKc8STiM-wuSStFfXSg05wDo3yrHB3ufxb=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 1,
      "relative_time_description": "in the last week",
      "text": "Google keep up with your bad services, lack of support and accountability. Your are doing a great job at creating your downfall. Remember technology changes rapidly, competition is strong. Who was once at the top will change in the future. Look at Nokia.",
      "time": 1758026262,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Yashaswi Verma",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105360031535707570077/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUa8UHkSGjBSuHosbbG9N_y6Q0PbIDTaNS51t5AHyvVcNNWO0MYnQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "Had a great time today. I went to the club and it had really great cocktails. The food was also really good. Overall, I had a great fun with my friends. The only problem was that the place is usually very crowded.",
      "time": 1755008960,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Simon Leaver",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102334085932590158209/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9gELSUGQ_3FJlwnkhpOJlL-CHR_5kyGQK5wEF3cs-JAf8TA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "5 months ago",
      "text": "Following a recent purchase this week, of a Vehicle from Lee of Prestige Trade Port Melbourne, I felt I should share my experience. Being in business for 28 years and a Reg. Practitioner with the VBA, Professionally I can not speak highly enough about Lee's professionalism and assistants from my initial enquiry, meeting, and my decision in purchasing the Vehicle that best suited my needs. Lee went out of his way to assist, disclose all my questions and further details about the Vehicle. To Lee's credit he accepted my txt msgs and questions on a Sunday afternoon. Nothing was a problem or an issue, which conveyed to me trust and confidence throughout the purchase.\nUpon pickup the Vehicle was immaculately presented with a full tank of fuel.\nI anticipate the same content and confidence will continue with the running of the Vehicle.\nI would certainly recommend Lee and Team, furthermore I will be doing further business in the future for my next purchase.\nKudos to you Lee, job well done.\nagain Thank you.\nSincerest Regards,\nSimon L.ðŸ‘Œ",
      "time": 1744930084,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Flo Yeow",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101597484841229205770/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCED0nHINoONtoIhYrg_037nt9gzG8G4ZOxJ3RLinEhCioWYU8hrs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 years ago",
      "text": "This is the Sales side of the couple of offices that Google has in Sydney. The engineering side is nicer but this is nice too.\n\nStraightforward set up, in a single column building, stairs and lift in the middle, and everything else around it. Professional baristas at The Press are really lovely people, and when I visited the dining hall was serving Carbonara on a cheese wheel. Make sure you stand at the rooftop balcony and enjoy the breeze and view of the surroundings.\n\nWith such gorgeous amenities and benefits, what's there not to like about working here.",
      "time": 1670547584,
      "translated": false
    }
  ],
